# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

- [!] Create firewall rule
- [!] Handle Application Update
- [!] Handle Table on blog post

## [0.1.9] - 2022
- Add World Map Visualization
- Add Account Manager
- Add Apps View
- Add Whois
- Add History (Audit Log)
- Add Cloudflare ips
- Add Biometric Authentication
- Add Light Theme
- Correct some bugs
- Upgrade to Gradle 8 and to JDK 17

## [0.1.8] - 2023-04-09
- Change layout depending on token permissions
- Refresh Token Permissions
- ImageDownloader Settings
- Improve Error Handling
- Review all listener
- Better back handler
- Fix some bug (specially on start)

## [0.1.7] - 2022-08-29
- Add the possibility to use revocable token
- Fix bug when dashboard was not updated when changing zone
- Fix bug when back is pressed
- Test Token before adding it
- Alert are now better displayed
- Better image loader + cache

## [0.1.6] - 2022-07-22
- Add application crash report

## [0.1.5] - 2022-07-03
- Fix some bug
- Fix bug on cloudflare status
- Add possibility to edit dns record
- Add community
- Add "moved" icon status
- Clicking the zone status icon now display the status
- Improve image loading + cache
- Add Application Log

## [0.1.4] - 2022-04-06
- Improve Performance
- Add origin Certificates
- Add Always Online
- Add Mirage
- Add Polish
- Add WebP
- Add Privacy Pass
- Add HTTP2 & HTTP3
- Add History (you can now use back)
- Add Country Table
- Dashboard now keep data 5m before refreshing
- Add view behind dns record when swiping it
- Add Dark Amoled Theme

## [0.1.3] - 2022-02-13
- Improve the chart for too recent domain
- Logout Improvement
- Theme Improvement
- Fix Synchronized chart
- Fix Crash when view changed too quickly
- Add firewall rules
- Add Chart lookup (long press)
- Add help on login screen
- Add Rate/Feedback
- Add Cloudflare Blog
- Add Cloudflare Blog Notifications
- Add Daily stats
- Add App related link

## [0.1.2] - 2021-12-29
- Add Notification View
- Add Early Hints (Beta)
- Add Auto Minify
- Add Threats Chart
- Fix Under Attack Mode
- Fix Browser Cache TTL
- Fix Caching Level
- Fix Change Encryption Mode
- Fix Performance Cached Chart
- Fix Startup Crash when remember zone is enable on android 10+
- Improve CloudFlare Status
- Notify when a plan is not enough to use this api request

## [0.1.1] - 2021-11-26
- Can now add DNS Record
- Can now delete DNS Record
- Fix "pending" status logo
- Add CloudFlare status

## [0.1.0]
- Initial Release
